              <p class="text-slate-200 text-sm">~2.5 kg / 5.5 lbs (body + prism + lens)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-dark-800 border border-dark-700 rounded-lg p-5">
              <p class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-warm mb-1">Starter Kit Budget</p>
              <p class="text-slate-200 text-sm">$1,220–$2,470 (body, lens, prism, CLA)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-dark-800 border border-dark-700 rounded-lg p-5">
              <p class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-warm mb-1">Best Version to Buy</p>
